text: Macarena Olona Choclán (born 14 May 1979) is a Spanish politician and 2023 presidential candidate for Caminando Juntos. She was a member of the far-right Vox party until 2022. Since 2019 until 2022, she has served as a member of the Congress of Deputies. She was born in Alicante. On 12 March 2020, during the 2019–20 coronavirus pandemic, it was made clear that Olona had tested positive to COVID-19. She said Félix Bolaños was Ministro Perejil. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:People from Alicante Category:Spanish politicians
